React
==============================
To solve `javascript heap memory` full error or to increase size allocation to node as default heap memory allocated to node is 1.7 GB and some project need much more heap memory
                                     write in package.json     "start": "react-scripts --max_old_space_size=4096 start",
                                                               "build": "react-scripts --max_old_space_size=4096 build",
                                                               
                                                               
                                                               To increase memory to 4GB 
Used react-image-file-resizer package to send image and get converted images with different formats in base64 format
